    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction</h2>The Cesspit是一款第一人称恐怖冒险游戏，游戏的背景设定在幽暗深邃的下水道中。<br><br>你必须探索迷宫般的通道，下水道里的变态居民在这里徘徊并试图逃跑。<br>您必须依靠蜡烛的光亮指引方向，应对黑暗中潜伏的威胁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003470/extras/e72cc30df6089ed1ca986d6a3e8a7154.poster.avif?t=1726228637\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003470/extras/e72cc30df6089ed1ca986d6a3e8a7154.webm?t=1726228637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003470/extras/e72cc30df6089ed1ca986d6a3e8a7154.mp4?t=1726228637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2>当主人公睁开眼睛时，他发现自己身处一个陌生的环境。<br>幽闭恐怖的封闭环境迫使他冒险深入寻找出路，但这里扭曲的居民并不欢迎他。<br><br>您必须探索这个被遗弃的废墟，穿越重重障碍，找到出路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003470/extras/f69dea6eeb5e720d492072061dea5175.poster.avif?t=1726228637\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003470/extras/f69dea6eeb5e720d492072061dea5175.webm?t=1726228637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003470/extras/f69dea6eeb5e720d492072061dea5175.mp4?t=1726228637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 区域黑暗而复杂。<br></li><li> 有可怕的景象和声音。<br></li><li> 进入下一个区域需要先决条件。<br></li><li> 下水道里有许多居民，他们都不友好。<br></li><li> 与具有不同特征的生物打交道。</li></ul>",
